# Sample data
The following are data used in the unit testing and sample executiion of RRASSLER.  These folders are copied out of the following sources.  _Note that RRASSLER will not archive all pieces of information contained in these source data._

## Iowa
Sample data from the RAS2FIM workflow at https://github.com/NOAA-OWP/ras2fim

## Texas
